    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Maybe the fact that the urlSync is currently thought as a widget was the wrong move initially. It is a very special widget, with no render, that must be called last (and we already add some code to ensure that).\n\nMaybe we should move the whole url-generation part as a core part of instantsearch, so every widget can access it and be able to generate urls. In that case the `urlSync` widget would only do the synchronisation of the current helper state with the browser url, but all url-handling will be deported inside instantsearch directly.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-15T10:35:10Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/248#issuecomment-148346550",
