    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Maybe the fact that the urlSync is currently thought as a widget was the wrong move initially. \n\nNow that I think of yes this would be easier to have everything url inside the instantsearch.js. Basically it's about instantiating the urlSync widget if urlSync: {} is passed as instantsearch params.\n\nThis will allow us to remove the __init lifecycle trick that was only done for the urlSync widget (allow configuring/init order to be modified)\n\n:+1: \n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-15T12:06:37Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/248#issuecomment-148367301",
